00:15:45.140 --> 00:15:50.659
there's a lot of people that are involved to make sure that we're making clinically appropriate

00:15:50.659 --> 00:15:57.780
assumptions to then finally get to, you know, how we get to our data set, right. And so it's

00:15:57.780 --> 00:16:03.539
probably a lot longer in the real world data space than than perhaps others, but I don't have a whole

