honest, I just kind of like get it done and try to do it in a manner that I don't have to do it.

00:16:28.580 --> 00:16:33.460
Like repetitively try to build on knowledge. And is that something that you have to

00:16:35.859 --> 00:16:39.940
communicate with other folks in the business about or do they usually understand?

00:16:40.900 --> 00:16:44.419
I know that there's a lot that goes into, you know, the pre-cooking.

00:16:46.340 --> 00:16:52.820
Yeah, I mean, I think that goes to, I guess, to go back to Rachel's question about what gets me

00:16:52.820 --> 00:16:58.020
excited, right? So what gets me excited is that great, all these businesses are very interested

00:16:58.020 --> 00:17:04.099
