so that you can scale your operations. So you can throw more people at it, but

00:18:40.180 --> 00:18:44.180
when you're throwing people at it, you're providing more company value rather than

00:18:44.180 --> 00:18:52.020
trying to wade through the mud with increasingly large data sets or increasingly complex data sets.

